    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1075">
<l>accamē kīḻkaḷa tācāra mecca </l>
<l>mavāvuṇṭē luṇṭāñ ciṟitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(The principle of) behaviour in the mean is chiefly fear; if not, hope of gain, to some extent.</l>
            </lg>
